Dialog.text: Commander Dahl. This is William Yu, acting chairman of the TranStar Board of Directors.
Of course. My authentication sign is Zeta. Invictus. Emperor. Tangerine.
You must secure every piece of Cobalt clearance level technology and research aboard Talos I. Then eliminate all TranStar personnel.
Payment will be deposited into six separate Benelux accounts... after you transmit evidence of success.
We strongly advise deploying your technical officer to a station router inside the firewalls first.
Ideal site would be the Cargo Bay.
You will destroy this transmission aft-
